cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NE, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on monitoring and managing large-scale distributed computing systems.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for time-series forecasting using clustering and centroids.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with system management and resource allocation.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also possible categories as the paper proposes a machine learning-based approach for forecasting.
